article_title: Many carriers seeking higher prices for 2016 health plans
article_text:
Many carriers seeking higher prices for 2016 health plans High medical costs cited for increases

Photo: Express-News File Photo People line up to enroll for health insurance under the Affordable...

Significant rate increases are being proposed for some health insurance plans sold in San Antonio as carriers nationwide struggle with higher-than-expected medical costs incurred during the first year of open enrollment.
